2026-04-29T11:52:00.037+00:00 **Root cause identified.** The `orders` table has 500 million rows but only a primary key index on `id`. All other columns (`user_id`, `order_date`, `amount`, `status`) have no indexes, forcing full table scans on every non-PK query.

